# MongoDB sizing agent

- Phase 2 deliverable: `cases/{useCase}/outputs/data-model.md` (approval required before seed/Docker).
- Phase 4: `sizing-report.md` / `.json` from `scripts/size_from_dbstats.py` only.
- `mongodb_indexes.json`: compound indexes with no redundant prefix indexes on same collection/options.
- Seed: 500 documents per top-level collection; embedded arrays sized from `outputs/sizing_inputs.json` embedded.avgCardinality.
- macOS local MongoDB: Colima + `docker compose` (see `scripts/run_local_stack.sh`).
